	<title>Darkness Within II by MollyandArthur [R]</title>
	<link>http://www.siye.co.uk/siye/viewstory.php?sid=130202</link>
	<description>Sequel to Darkness Within. This story begins the night before Harry&apos;s fifth year at Hogwarts. Canon couples accurate to JKR. The romance between Harry and Ginny will develop slowly due to their ages. Please note rating and warnings. </description>
